reviewText: My two years old daughter, can't sleep with out this book. It's good for little girls. U will love it.

This is such a great deal! My kids never get tired of Dora and Diego.

Diego episodes:
Freddie the fruit bat saves Halloween
Alicia saves the crocodile
Diego and Dora help baby monarch get to the festival
Manatee's mermaid rescue

Dora episodes:
Boo!
To the monkey bars
The missing piece
The big storm

My 2 grands love anything Dora and Diego. They have watched these dvds over and over again.
Will be purchasing more in the future.
Great fun to watch with my grandkids.  They are so interested that they ignore us when whatching.  "Catchy" tunes that we can jump and dance to makes it fun for all of us; kids and adults alike.

It is  our 2 year old grandson's favorite DVD!
He is still watching it even though it's  over a month past Halloween.
I sent it to my nephew in Florida for his birthday. He received it in plenty of time and loved it. I saved money too!
